Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.80,0:00:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.63,0:00:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.34,0:00:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.31,0:00:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.09,0:00:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.90,0:00:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.57,0:00:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.94,0:00:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.04,0:01:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.15,0:01:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.65,0:01:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.09,0:01:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.76,0:01:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.13,0:01:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.67,0:01:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.00,0:01:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.61,0:01:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.85,0:01:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這要送給我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.88,0:01:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.53,0:02:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可愛的別針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.33,0:02:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳喜歡這個別針嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.36,0:02:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好高興,可是五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.70,0:02:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼要送我聖誕禮物呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.54,0:02:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.81,0:02:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.41,0:02:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.68,0:02:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,不瞞你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.78,0:02:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我一直很喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.85,0:02:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.43,0:02:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.10,0:02:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好危險的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.77,0:02:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員來到一刻館\N轉眼間已經過了一個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.61,0:02:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,街上充滿著聖誕節氣氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.41,0:02:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我花了大半生活費買的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.31,0:03:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要想辦法交給她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.68,0:03:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#02戀愛的火花閃閃!響子喜歡誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.63,0:03:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,握手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,握手,握手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.83,0:03:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,握手啦,握手\N你不會握手嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.94,0:03:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.07,0:03:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.87,0:03:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,吃飯囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.34,0:03:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准吃!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.41,0:03:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准吃!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.68,0:03:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員\N這傢伙是不是有點癡呆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.55,0:03:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這太難了啦\N因為我什麼都沒教牠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.19,0:03:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.19,0:03:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賢太郎!\N你又在這裡鬼混了啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.33,0:03:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不快點去寫功課!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.60,0:03:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.80,0:03:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,他難得出去工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然這麼快就回來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.21,0:04:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.92,0:04:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.32,0:04:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可愛的狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.55,0:04:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小白,小白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.89,0:04:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,這個金三郎糖果給你吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.76,0:04:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!惣一郎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.66,0:04:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這隻狗真可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.43,0:04:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.47,0:04:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他到底在做什麼工作啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.74,0:04:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浩太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.54,0:04:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浩太郎\N我等一下拿魚骨頭給你吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.51,0:04:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小白…浩太郎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.49,0:04:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的名字叫惣一郎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.16,0:04:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,米奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,米奇,這個給你吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.53,0:04:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.06,0:04:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,我在叫妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.17,0:04:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到了,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.84,0:05:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好兇喔,妳怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.54,0:05:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,沒什麼\N有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.14,0:05:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說下午會下雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這棟公寓漏水漏得很嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.31,0:05:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前那個管理員什麼都不做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.15,0:05:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.16,0:05:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.33,0:05:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把自己的名字當作什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.96,0:05:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到牠居然這麼隨便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.13,0:05:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如趁現在\N請賢太郎訓練牠好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.57,0:05:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎\N希望你能明白我的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.62,0:05:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子現在剛好在這屋頂上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.42,0:05:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她今年幾歲了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有男朋友呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.33,0:06:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳…妳是什麼時候來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.47,0:06:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼時候來的都無所謂吧,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.17,0:06:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本來想來跟你買泡麵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.68,0:06:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來我賺到了\N你會免費送給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰要送妳啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.08,0:06:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這個月得靠這些泡麵維生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.55,0:06:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.78,0:06:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.72,0:06:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝啦,你真是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.19,0:06:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快出去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.39,0:06:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你喜歡的那個天花板啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.40,0:06:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天花板怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她有男朋友喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,笨狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.20,0:07:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真好命,管理員那麼疼你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.64,0:07:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,她居然有男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.51,0:07:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨狗,她真的有男朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.81,0:07:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.01,0:07:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這麼小氣,快點告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.85,0:07:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點告訴我啊,你這隻笨狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.55,0:07:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不告訴我的話,我就不離開這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.19,0:07:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,屋頂修好了沒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.27,0:07:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳有聽到嗎?快下大雨了\N修好了沒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.01,0:07:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會是跌下來了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,這樣會感冒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.94,0:08:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳睡得好熟喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.31,0:08:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,現在是把禮物\N拿給她的大好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.15,0:09:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.26,0:09:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.46,0:09:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,…惣一郎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.30,0:09:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下雨了,我得快去收衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.70,0:09:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是屋頂啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.08,0:09:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.14,0:09:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下雨了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.97,0:10:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然打了我一巴掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般只是摸一下胸部\N會甩人一巴掌嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.97,0:10:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.81,0:10:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定她對那個\N叫惣一郎的人很忠貞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.38,0:10:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賢太郎,你功課寫完了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.99,0:10:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寫完了,雨停了之後\N我可以跟惣一郎玩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.83,0:10:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.26,0:10:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雨快點停吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.35,0:10:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,綁架!綁架!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.25,0:10:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要鬼叫!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.05,0:10:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我問你,你認識惣一郎嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.46,0:10:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牠是我的朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.82,0:10:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!他…他是小學生嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得牠年紀蠻大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.66,0:11:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是個怎麼樣的男人?告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你伸手出來幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.84,0:11:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.74,0:11:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要好好珍惜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰要你的泡麵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該知道我要什麼吧,快拿來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下到公園來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我讓你和惣一郎見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.02,0:12:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是惣一郎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.30,0:12:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.77,0:12:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我給你取的名字\N是我最重要的人的名字喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.01,0:12:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.48,0:12:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好想變成那條狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁現在!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.39,0:13:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們來好好狂歡一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.12,0:13:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要辦聖誕派對嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.52,0:13:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,兩千圓吃到飽喝到飽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.53,0:13:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來的都是自己人,很輕鬆喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.26,0:13:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶爾輕鬆一下也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.14,0:13:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要不要也來我們店裡?\N男生三千圓,很便宜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.11,0:13:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別來煩我,我現在忙著考試\N可沒有閒工夫跟你們玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.61,0:13:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就不勉強你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.65,0:13:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.18,0:13:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,兩千圓對不對?\N錢給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.05,0:13:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.16,0:13:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶爾也要輕鬆一下,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.70,0:13:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼等你們來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.96,0:13:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.67,0:13:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個月的生活費\N完全花光光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.47,0:13:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且是為了這種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.84,0:13:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好久沒有參加派對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.75,0:14:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在…只能趁現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.05,0:14:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.42,0:14:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.45,0:14:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,是這樣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.29,0:14:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.73,0:14:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖誕禮物,送給妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼都別說,收下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.27,0:14:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個要送給我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.70,0:14:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.71,0:14:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是摸彩抽中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.01,0:14:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,為什麼要送給我呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.51,0:14:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我最喜歡管理員了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.11,0:14:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝,我也最喜歡賢太郎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.55,0:14:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.22,0:14:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.59,0:14:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,真的真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.46,0:14:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重考生,你找我有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係,等一下再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩子真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.98,0:15:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算一次也好\N我好想學他那樣把話說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.70,0:15:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,好好地玩玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.61,0:15:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天晚上真的很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.97,0:15:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.64,0:15:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.64,0:15:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.01,0:15:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你換座位好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.45,0:15:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳好漂亮喔,真是個大美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.05,0:15:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼漂亮的美女\N當管理員太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.46,0:15:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時鐘坡的大美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.76,0:16:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳有男朋友吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.13,0:16:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,我沒有男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.33,0:16:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有男朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.80,0:16:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我來追妳好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.71,0:16:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔\N你要拋棄老婆跟孩子嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.38,0:16:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我通通不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.78,0:16:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只如此,只要能跟響子在一起\N我死都願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要死自己去死,你這個不良中年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.65,0:16:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要換位子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.32,0:16:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.62,0:16:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.09,0:16:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,大叔我好寂寞喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.80,0:16:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中年人真討厭,我來保護妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.17,0:16:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.13,0:16:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.47,0:16:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.90,0:16:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.31,0:16:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.74,0:16:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你的臭手拿開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.15,0:16:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員要跟我結婚\N不要隨便碰她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.18,0:16:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.32,0:16:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個蠻登對的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.75,0:17:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,很速配很速配…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.37,0:17:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.70,0:17:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才九點而已耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.34,0:17:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能把公寓放著不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.44,0:17:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.74,0:17:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放鬆時間結束,繼續努力用功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.95,0:17:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次一定要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.99,0:17:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.22,0:17:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我會帶他回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,重考生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.19,0:17:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路上不能對管理員\N毛手毛腳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.34,0:17:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,換我來背吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.10,0:17:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要,我討厭讓男生背
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.74,0:17:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係,他很輕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.01,0:18:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.01,0:18:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果還是沒能交給她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.98,0:18:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這明明是很簡單的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.65,0:18:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是沒用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.84,0:19:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滾出去!滾出我的房間!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.05,0:19:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼啊?什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滾出去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大色狼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.03,0:19:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,開門!\N這明明是我的房間啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開門!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.40,0:19:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開門!喂!開門!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.87,0:19:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.07,0:20:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,是這樣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.21,0:20:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫不醒耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.62,0:20:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她已經醉得不醒人事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.15,0:20:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.92,0:20:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.80,0:21:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老天爺沒有放棄我\N要交給她的話得趁現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.41,0:21:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.64,0:21:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.81,0:21:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是說茶\N太濃的話會變得苦苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.38,0:21:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說…說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.79,0:21:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼…為什麼說不出口呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.19,0:21:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.23,0:21:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.40,0:21:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要玩點遊戲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.50,0:21:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.98,0:21:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是今天賢太郎送給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.75,0:21:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說是聖誕禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.55,0:22:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,不能再這樣下去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.59,0:22:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.33,0:22:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.53,0:22:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.70,0:22:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.87,0:22:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡不是廁所嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.18,0:22:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,再忍耐一下喔,我帶你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.49,0:23:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.03,0:23:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下雪了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.54,0:23:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天一定要交給她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.46,0:23:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕了\N五代的大學聯考終於要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.27,0:23:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是大家一直吵他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.90,0:23:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.77,0:24:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『暗夜中心跳不已\N和響子單獨相處』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.21,0:24:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連鐘台的鐘聲都響起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.65,0:24:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.13,0:24:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何妳能如此若無其事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.41,0:24:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光只是眨個眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.38,0:24:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能讓我悸動不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.48,0:24:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使我身陷險境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.73,0:24:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明已經可以相愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.23,0:25:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偏偏時機還不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.74,0:25:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我快要忍受不了\N快要變成了愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.25,0:25:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是痛苦的折磨

